{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778432122451,"sessionID":"ses_1ed3dd493ffeWL8kHA9OSsAIAK","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"apply_patch","callID":"call_Ln9uG9lRXVEGOJ8mA8T6rWIH","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"patchText":"*** Begin Patch\n*** Add File: /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n+The requested obsolete metabolite process terms are represented as obsolete in the ontology with the requested replacement/consider metadata. I also cleaned the obsolete stanzas to remove retained synonyms and corrected the galactonate obsoletion comment typo.\n+\n+Changes committed in PR #<NN>.\n*** Add File: /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENTS.md\n+## Summary\n+\n+Addressed issue #31978 by cleaning the obsolete stanzas for the requested grouping terms:\n+\n+- `GO:0019584 obsolete galactonate catabolic process`: retained `consider` links to `GO:0034194` and `GO:0034195`, removed obsolete-term synonyms, and fixed the obsoletion comment typo.\n+- `GO:0046180 obsolete ketogluconate biosynthetic process`: retained `replaced_by: GO:0046179` and removed obsolete-term synonyms.\n+- `GO:0046181 obsolete ketogluconate catabolic process`: retained `replaced_by: GO:0019524` and removed obsolete-term synonyms.\n+\n+## Rationale\n+\n+The issue requests removal of unnecessary grouping terms, with replacements or candidate replacements supplied by the requester. The ontology already contained the requested obsolete status and replacement/consider metadata; this change brings the obsolete stanzas into line with GO obsoletion practice by removing synonyms from obsolete terms and fixing a typo in the obsoletion reason.\n+\n+## Validation\n+\n+- Pre-validation before editing: `make travis_build` passed.\n+- Post-edit validation: `make travis_build` passed.\n+- Internal ontology reference check found no active GO stanzas depending on the obsolete target IDs beyond the obsolete stanzas/replacement metadata.\n+- Attempted direct annotation checks with `runoak -i amigo: associations`, but the local `runoak` installation failed before query execution due to a Python dependency mismatch: `AttributeError: type object 'Format' has no attribute 'JSON'`. The issue text/comment supplied annotation impact information: one EcoCyc annotation for `GO:0019584` should move to `GO:0034195`; no annotations/cross-references were reported for `GO:0046180` and `GO:0046179`, and `GO:0046181` should be replaced by `GO:0019524`.\n+\n+## Checklist\n+\n+- [x] PLAN: Issue context reviewed; requested obsoletions/replacements are clear.\n+- [x] PRE-VALIDATION: Current ontology validated before changes.\n+- [x] RESEARCH: N/A; no new literature-derived definitions or references were introduced.\n+- [x] TERM-SEARCH: Target and replacement GO terms inspected with `obo-grep.pl`.\n+- [x] DESIGN-PATTERNS: N/A; no new terms or logical definitions were added.\n+- [x] EDITS: Terms were checked out to `terms/`, edited there, and checked back into `src/ontology/go-edit.obo`.\n+- [x] RELATIONSHIPS: Obsolete terms retain no `is_a`, `relationship`, or `intersection_of` axioms; replacement/consider metadata preserved.\n+- [x] SPECIALIZED-EDITS: Term obsoletion guidance followed; chemical-entity guidance consulted because the terms involve named metabolites.\n+- [x] METADATA: Obsolete stanzas retain namespace, obsolete definitions, obsoletion comments, `term_tracker_item`, and appropriate `consider`/`replaced_by` tags.\n+- [x] AUTOMATED-VALIDATION: Post-edit `make travis_build` passed.\n+- [x] REFERENCE-VALIDATION: N/A; no new references were introduced.\n+- [x] CHANGES-COMMITTED: Committed local ontology changes only.\n*** End Patch"},"output":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\nA PR_COMMENTS.md","metadata":{"diff":"Index: /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,3 @@\n+The requested obsolete metabolite process terms are represented as obsolete in the ontology with the requested replacement/consider metadata. I also cleaned the obsolete stanzas to remove retained synonyms and corrected the galactonate obsoletion comment typo.\n+\n+Changes committed in PR #<NN>.\n\nIndex: /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,33 @@\n+## Summary\n+\n+Addressed issue #31978 by cleaning the obsolete stanzas for the requested grouping terms:\n+\n+- `GO:0019584 obsolete galactonate catabolic process`: retained `consider` links to `GO:0034194` and `GO:0034195`, removed obsolete-term synonyms, and fixed the obsoletion comment typo.\n+- `GO:0046180 obsolete ketogluconate biosynthetic process`: retained `replaced_by: GO:0046179` and removed obsolete-term synonyms.\n+- `GO:0046181 obsolete ketogluconate catabolic process`: retained `replaced_by: GO:0019524` and removed obsolete-term synonyms.\n+\n+## Rationale\n+\n+The issue requests removal of unnecessary grouping terms, with replacements or candidate replacements supplied by the requester. The ontology already contained the requested obsolete status and replacement/consider metadata; this change brings the obsolete stanzas into line with GO obsoletion practice by removing synonyms from obsolete terms and fixing a typo in the obsoletion reason.\n+\n+## Validation\n+\n+- Pre-validation before editing: `make travis_build` passed.\n+- Post-edit validation: `make travis_build` passed.\n+- Internal ontology reference check found no active GO stanzas depending on the obsolete target IDs beyond the obsolete stanzas/replacement metadata.\n+- Attempted direct annotation checks with `runoak -i amigo: associations`, but the local `runoak` installation failed before query execution due to a Python dependency mismatch: `AttributeError: type object 'Format' has no attribute 'JSON'`. The issue text/comment supplied annotation impact information: one EcoCyc annotation for `GO:0019584` should move to `GO:0034195`; no annotations/cross-references were reported for `GO:0046180` and `GO:0046179`, and `GO:0046181` should be replaced by `GO:0019524`.\n+\n+## Checklist\n+\n+- [x] PLAN: Issue context reviewed; requested obsoletions/replacements are clear.\n+- [x] PRE-VALIDATION: Current ontology validated before changes.\n+- [x] RESEARCH: N/A; no new literature-derived definitions or references were introduced.\n+- [x] TERM-SEARCH: Target and replacement GO terms inspected with `obo-grep.pl`.\n+- [x] DESIGN-PATTERNS: N/A; no new terms or logical definitions were added.\n+- [x] EDITS: Terms were checked out to `terms/`, edited there, and checked back into `src/ontology/go-edit.obo`.\n+- [x] RELATIONSHIPS: Obsolete terms retain no `is_a`, `relationship`, or `intersection_of` axioms; replacement/consider metadata preserved.\n+- [x] SPECIALIZED-EDITS: Term obsoletion guidance followed; chemical-entity guidance consulted because the terms involve named metabolites.\n+- [x] METADATA: Obsolete stanzas retain namespace, obsolete definitions, obsoletion comments, `term_tracker_item`, and appropriate `consider`/`replaced_by` tags.\n+- [x] AUTOMATED-VALIDATION: Post-edit `make travis_build` passed.\n+- [x] REFERENCE-VALIDATION: N/A; no new references were introduced.\n+- [x] CHANGES-COMMITTED: Committed local ontology changes only.\n\n","files":[{"filePath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","relativePath":"ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","type":"add","patch":"Index: /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,3 @@\n+The requested obsolete metabolite process terms are represented as obsolete in the ontology with the requested replacement/consider metadata. I also cleaned the obsolete stanzas to remove retained synonyms and corrected the galactonate obsoletion comment typo.\n+\n+Changes committed in PR #<NN>.\n","additions":3,"deletions":0},{"filePath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENTS.md","relativePath":"PR_COMMENTS.md","type":"add","patch":"Index: /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,33 @@\n+## Summary\n+\n+Addressed issue #31978 by cleaning the obsolete stanzas for the requested grouping terms:\n+\n+- `GO:0019584 obsolete galactonate catabolic process`: retained `consider` links to `GO:0034194` and `GO:0034195`, removed obsolete-term synonyms, and fixed the obsoletion comment typo.\n+- `GO:0046180 obsolete ketogluconate biosynthetic process`: retained `replaced_by: GO:0046179` and removed obsolete-term synonyms.\n+- `GO:0046181 obsolete ketogluconate catabolic process`: retained `replaced_by: GO:0019524` and removed obsolete-term synonyms.\n+\n+## Rationale\n+\n+The issue requests removal of unnecessary grouping terms, with replacements or candidate replacements supplied by the requester. The ontology already contained the requested obsolete status and replacement/consider metadata; this change brings the obsolete stanzas into line with GO obsoletion practice by removing synonyms from obsolete terms and fixing a typo in the obsoletion reason.\n+\n+## Validation\n+\n+- Pre-validation before editing: `make travis_build` passed.\n+- Post-edit validation: `make travis_build` passed.\n+- Internal ontology reference check found no active GO stanzas depending on the obsolete target IDs beyond the obsolete stanzas/replacement 